{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01Wwqnwxr5nWEsa7JVeguQCH","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Now I have a complete understanding of the project. Let me compile a comprehensive report:\n\n## BudgetView-Tauri: Complete Project State Analysis\n\n### Project Overview\nThis is a rewrite of BudgetView (personal budget management software) using **Tauri 2 + SvelteKit + Svelte 5 + SQLite**. The project is in **Phase 1 (MVP)** with scaffolding complete and core MVP features partially implemented.\n\n---\n\n### Directory Structure & Files\n\n#### Root Directory\n**Location:** `/home/jeremy/Documents/budgetview-tauri/`\n\nKey files:\n- `package.json` - Frontend dependencies & build scripts\n- `vite.config.ts` - Vite configuration with Tauri dev host setup\n- `svelte.config.js` - SvelteKit static adapter configuration\n- `tsconfig.json` - TypeScript configuration with strict mode enabled\n- `src/app.css` - TailwindCSS 4 theme with dark mode colors\n- `src/app.html` - HTML template (lang=\"fr\")\n\n---\n\n### Frontend Architecture\n\n#### **src/lib/types/index.ts**\nComplete TypeScript interfaces for:\n- `Account` - Bank accounts (checking, savings, credit card, cash)\n- `BudgetSeries` - Budget categories with budget_area (income/recurring/variable/extras/savings/transfers)\n- `SubSeries` - Subcategories\n- `Transaction` - Individual transactions with categorization\n- `MonthlyBudget` - Monthly budget targets per series\n- `BudgetLineItem` - Aggregated budget view (planned vs actual)\n- `Project` & `ProjectItem` - Savings goals/projects\n- `DashboardSummary` - Key metrics for dashboard\n\n#### **src/lib/utils/format.ts**\n- `formatCurrency()` - French EUR formatting\n- `formatDate()` - French date formatting (DD/MM/YYYY)\n- `formatMonth()` - Localized month/year display\n- Constants: `ACCOUNT_TYPE_LABELS`, `BUDGET_AREA_LABELS`, `BUDGET_AREA_COLORS`\n\n#### **src/lib/stores/** (Svelte 5 reactive stores using `$state`)\n\n**db.ts:**\n- `getDb()` - Singleton database connection to `sqlite:budgetview.db`\n- `query<T>()` - SELECT queries with type safety\n- `execute()` - INSERT/UPDATE/DELETE operations\n\n**accounts.ts - AccountStore:**\n- State: `accounts[]`, `loading`, `error`\n- Methods: `load()`, `create()`, `update()`, `remove()`, `getBalance()`, `totalBalance` (computed)\n\n**transactions.ts - TransactionStore:**\n- State: `transactions[]`, `loading`, `error`, `search`, `filterAccountId`, `filterSeriesId`\n- Methods: `load()` (with filtering), `create()`, `update()`, `categorize()` (with auto-categorization learning), `remove()`\n\n**budget.ts - BudgetStore:**\n- State: `series[]`, `monthlyBudgets[]`, `budgetLines[]`, `loading`, `error`, `year`, `month`\n- Methods: `loadSeries()`, `loadBudgetView()`, `createSeries()`, `updateSeries()`, `removeSeries()`, `setMonthlyBudget()`\n- Computed: `groupedByArea` (grouped by budget_area), `totalPlanned`, `totalActual`\n\n#### **src/lib/components/**\n\n**Sidebar.svelte:**\n- Responsive navigation sidebar with BudgetView branding (blue \"B\" logo)\n- 6 main nav items: Dashboard, Accounts, Transactions, Budget, Analysis, Projects\n- Active link highlighting using `$page.url.pathname`\n- Version display (v0.1.0)\n\n---\n\n### Routes & Pages\n\nAll pages include French `<svelte:head><title>` tags.\n\n#### **src/routes/+layout.svelte**\n- Master layout with sidebar + main content area\n- Flex layout: sidebar (fixed width) + main (flex-1, overflow-y-auto with padding)\n- Imports global `app.css`\n\n#### **src/routes/dashboard/+page.svelte** ✅ (Implemented)\n**Summary Cards:** 4 cards showing:\n- Total balance (Wallet icon)\n- Month income (TrendingUp, green/income color)\n- Month expenses (TrendingDown, red/expense color)\n- Transaction count\n\n**Two-column grid:**\n1. **Accounts Section** - Lists all accounts with type badges and balances\n2. **Recent Transactions** - Last 10 transactions with date/label/amount\n\n**Budget Summary Section:**\n- Conditional: Only shown if budget series exist\n- Displays planned vs actual with progress bars (colored by over/under budget)\n\n**Data Loading:**\n- `onMount()` calls: `accountStore.load()`, `budgetStore.loadBudgetView()`\n- SQL queries for month income/expenses/count via `query()`\n- Recent transactions joined with account names\n\n#### **src/routes/accounts/+page.svelte** ✅ (Implemented)\n**Features:**\n- Total balance display at top\n- Account list cards with edit/delete buttons\n- Modal form for create/edit (name, type, bank, number, initial balance)\n- Account type dropdown using `ACCOUNT_TYPE_LABELS`\n- Responsive grid layout\n- Empty state with Landmark icon\n\n#### **src/routes/transactions/+page.svelte** ✅ (Implemented)\n**Features:**\n- Create/Edit modal form\n- Search bar (live search on Enter key)\n- Filter dropdowns: by account, by category (series)\n- Table view: Date | Label | Account | Category | Amount | Actions\n- Inline categorization popover (click category button to see dropdown)\n- Auto-categorization learning: Saves pattern + series_id to `categorization_rules` table\n- Edit/Delete buttons per row\n- Empty state with Upload icon\n\n**Categorization Logic:**\n- Extracts original_label.toUpperCase() as pattern\n- Upserts into `categorization_rules` with match_count increment\n- Learns from manual categorization for future auto-matching\n\n#### **src/routes/budget/+page.svelte** ✅ (Implemented)\n**Features:**\n- Month navigation (prev/next buttons)\n- Summary cards: Planned | Realized | Remainder\n- Grouped by budget area (income, recurring, variable, extras, savings, transfers)\n- Each category shows:\n  - Inline editable budget amount\n  - Progress bar (color-coded: green=under budget, orange=80%+, red=>100%)\n  - Planned vs Actual amounts\n- Pencil icon to edit series metadata\n- Create new category modal\n\n**Progress Logic:**\n- For income: `actual/planned * 100` (higher is better)\n- For expenses: `abs(actual)/abs(planned) * 100` (lower is better)\n- Over-budget detection and color coding\n\n#### **src/routes/analysis/+page.svelte** ⚠️ (Placeholder)\n- Minimal implementation: \"Pas encore de données\" placeholder\n- Prepared for Phase 2 (Charts section)\n\n#### **src/routes/projects/+page.svelte** ⚠️ (Placeholder)\n- Minimal implementation: \"Aucun projet\" placeholder\n- Prepared for Phase 3 (Projects/savings goals)\n\n---\n\n### Backend (Rust/Tauri)\n\n#### **src-tauri/src/lib.rs**\n```rust\npub fn run() {\n    tauri::Builder::default()\n        .plugin(tauri_plugin_sql with migrations)\n        .plugin(tauri_plugin_log)\n        .invoke_handler([greet])\n        .run()\n}\n```\n\n#### **src-tauri/src/main.rs**\n- Entry point calling `app_lib::run()`\n- Prevents extra console window on Windows\n\n#### **src-tauri/src/commands.rs**\n**Current Commands:**\n- `greet(name: &str) -> String` - Test command returning \"Bienvenue dans BudgetView, {name} !\"\n\n**TODO:** Need to implement actual commands:\n- Account CRUD\n- Transaction CRUD/import\n- Budget operations\n- Series management\n\n#### **src-tauri/src/db.rs**\n```rust\npub fn get_migrations() -> Vec<Migration>\n```\nReturns one migration:\n- Version: 1\n- Description: \"create_initial_tables\"\n- SQL: Loads from `migrations/001_initial_schema.sql`\n\n#### **src-tauri/migrations/001_initial_schema.sql**\nComplete SQLite schema with:\n\n**Core Tables:**\n1. **accounts** - Bank accounts (id, name, account_number, bank_name, account_type, currency, initial_balance, is_active, created_at)\n2. **budget_series** - Budget categories (id, name, budget_area, target_amount, day_of_month, is_active, description)\n3. **sub_series** - Subcategories (id, series_id FK, name)\n4. **transactions** - Individual transactions (id, account_id FK, date, label, original_label, amount, note, is_planned, series_id FK, sub_series_id FK, import_batch_id FK, fitid, created_at)\n5. **transaction_splits** - Multi-category transactions (id, transaction_id FK, series_id FK, amount, note)\n6. **monthly_budget** - Monthly targets per series (id, series_id FK, year, month, planned_amount, UNIQUE constraint)\n\n**Supporting Tables:**\n7. **import_batches** - For rollback capability (id, filename, format IN (ofx/qif/csv), account_id FK, transaction_count, imported_at)\n8. **recurring_transactions** - Templates for recurring transactions (id, account_id FK, label, amount, series_id FK, frequency, day_of_month, start_date, end_date, is_active)\n9. **projects** - Savings goals (id, name, target_amount, target_date, account_id FK, is_active)\n10. **project_items** - Project expenses (id, project_id FK, label, planned_amount, month, year, series_id FK)\n11. **tags** - Transaction tags (id, name UNIQUE)\n12. **transaction_tags** - Tagging junction (transaction_id FK, tag_id FK, PK both)\n13. **categorization_rules** - Auto-categorization patterns (id, pattern UNIQUE, series_id FK, sub_series_id FK, match_count, created_at)\n\n**Pragmas & Indexes:**\n- `PRAGMA journal_mode=WAL` (Write-Ahead Logging for concurrent access)\n- `PRAGMA foreign_keys=ON`\n- Indexes on: transactions.date, transactions.account_id, transactions.series_id, transactions.fitid, monthly_budget.year/month, project_items.project_id\n\n#### **src-tauri/Cargo.toml**\nDependencies:\n- `tauri` 2.10.3 - Core framework\n- `tauri-plugin-log` 2 - Logging\n- `tauri-plugin-sql` 2 (sqlite feature) - Database\n- `sqlx` 0.8 (sqlite + tokio) - SQL toolkit\n- `serde` + `serde_json` - JSON serialization\n- `chrono` 0.4 - Date/time handling\n- `log` 0.4 - Logging trait\n\n**Build Dependencies:**\n- `tauri-build` 2.5.6\n\n#### **src-tauri/tauri.conf.json**\n- App ID: `fr.budgetview.app`\n- Version: 0.1.0\n- Window: 1200x800 (min 900x600), resizable\n- DB preload: `sqlite:budgetview.db`\n- CSP: null (disabled)\n- Bundle targets: all platforms\n\n---\n\n### Package.json Dependencies\n\n**Frontend (Runtime):**\n- `@tauri-apps/api` 2.10.1 - Tauri command invocation & IPC\n- `@tauri-apps/plugin-sql` 2.3.2 - Database access\n- `lucide-svelte` 0.577.0 - 6 icons used (LayoutDashboard, Landmark, ArrowLeftRight, PieChart, BarChart3, FolderKanban, plus many more)\n\n**Dev Dependencies:**\n- `@sveltejs/kit` 2.50.2 - Framework\n- `@sveltejs/adapter-static` 3.0.0 - Static export adapter\n- `svelte` 5.51.0 - Component framework with runes\n- `@sveltejs/vite-plugin-svelte` 6.2.4\n- `@tauri-apps/cli` 2.10.1 - Build tooling\n- `tailwindcss` 4.2.1 - Styling\n- `@tailwindcss/vite` 4.2.1 - Vite plugin\n- `typescript` 5.9.3 - Type checking\n- `vite` 7.3.1 - Build tool\n- `svelte-check` 4.4.2 - Component type checking\n\n---\n\n### Styling\n\n#### TailwindCSS 4 Theme (src/app.css)\n**Color Variables (Dark Mode):**\n- `--color-bg-primary: #0f172a` (very dark blue)\n- `--color-bg-secondary: #1e293b` (dark blue/slate)\n- `--color-bg-card: #1e293b`\n- `--color-bg-hover: #334155` (slate)\n- `--color-border: #334155`\n- `--color-text-primary: #f1f5f9` (off-white)\n- `--color-text-secondary: #94a3b8` (light gray)\n- `--color-text-muted: #64748b` (medium gray)\n- `--color-accent: #3b82f6` (bright blue) / `--color-accent-hover: #2563eb`\n- `--color-success: #22c55e` (green)\n- `--color-warning: #f59e0b` (amber)\n- `--color-danger: #ef4444` (red)\n- `--color-income: #22c55e` (green)\n- `--color-expense: #ef4444` (red)\n\n**Global Styles:**\n- Font: Inter, system-ui (via @theme)\n- h-screen layout, scrollbar styling\n\n---\n\n### Build & Development Commands\n\nFrom `package.json`:\n```bash\nnpm run dev          # Start dev server (vite)\nnpm run build        # Build for production\nnpm run preview      # Preview built app\nnpm run check        # Type checking + svelte-check\nnpm run tauri        # Tauri CLI\n```\n\n**Tauri Dev Flow:**\n1. `beforeDevCommand: \"npm run dev\"` - Starts Vite dev server on port 1420\n2. `beforeBuildCommand: \"npm run build\"` - Builds frontend to `../build/`\n3. Frontend dist copied to `build/` directory\n\n---\n\n### Current Implementation Status\n\n#### ✅ Completed (MVP Phase 1)\n1. **Project Scaffolding** - Tauri 2 + SvelteKit + Svelte 5 + TailwindCSS 4\n2. **Database Schema** - Full SQLite schema with migrations\n3. **Type Definitions** - Complete TypeScript interfaces\n4. **Store/State Management** - Svelte 5 reactive stores with DB integration\n5. **Layout System** - Sidebar + main content layout\n6. **Dashboard Page** - Summary cards, account list, recent transactions, budget overview\n7. **Accounts Page** - CRUD accounts, balance display, modal form\n8. **Transactions Page** - List/search/filter, manual categorization, auto-categorization learning\n9. **Budget Page** - Monthly budget planning, progress visualization, series management\n10. **Utility Functions** - Currency/date formatting, label constants\n\n#### ⚠️ Placeholder/Partial\n1. **Analysis Page** - Skeleton only (Phase 2)\n2. **Projects Page** - Skeleton only (Phase 3)\n\n#### ❌ Not Yet Implemented\n1. **Tauri Commands** - Only `greet()` exists; need CRUD commands for actual backend queries\n2. **Import/Export** - OFX, QIF, CSV import logic (Phase 1 feature, critical for MVP)\n3. **Charts/Visualization** - Chart.js or Layercake integration (Phase 2)\n4. **Recurring Transactions** - Auto-detection logic (Phase 2)\n5. **Projects Management** - CRUD, goal tracking (Phase 3)\n6. **Multi-account Consolidation** - Summary views (Phase 3)\n7. **Encryption** - Password protection (Phase 3)\n8. **Mobile Responsiveness** - Tested but may need refinement\n9. **Error Handling** - Comprehensive error UI feedback\n10. **Accessibility** - ARIA labels, keyboard navigation polish\n\n---\n\n### Key Architectural Decisions\n\n1. **Offline-First** - SQLite embedded, no cloud dependency\n2. **Type-Safe** - TypeScript strict mode + Rust\n3. **Reactive UI** - Svelte 5 runes (`$state`, `$derived`)\n4. **DB Abstraction** - Store layer handles all DB queries\n5. **Auto-Categorization** - Pattern-based learning from user categorization\n6. **Budget Areas** - 6 categories (income/recurring/variable/extras/savings/transfers)\n7. **Monthly Budget Tracking** - Planned vs actual per category per month\n8. **WAL Mode** - SQLite Write-Ahead Logging for concurrency\n\n---\n\n### Next Priority Tasks (from CLAUDE.md Phase 1)\n\n1. **Implement Tauri Commands** for:\n   - Account CRUD (currently store-only)\n   - Transaction CRUD/import (currently store-only)\n   - Budget operations (currently store-only)\n\n2. **Add Import Feature** (OFX/QIF/CSV) - Critical for MVP\n3. **Refine Error Handling** - UI feedback for DB operations\n4. **Test Database Migrations** - Ensure schema creation works\n5. **Build & Package** - Test Tauri build for desktop platforms\n\n---\n\n### File Locations (Absolute Paths)\n\n**Frontend:**\n- `/home/jeremy/Documents/budgetview-tauri/src/lib/types/index.ts` - Types\n- `/home/jeremy/Documents/budgetview-tauri/src/lib/utils/format.ts` - Formatting\n- `/home/jeremy/Documents/budgetview-tauri/src/lib/stores/db.ts` - DB wrapper\n- `/home/jeremy/Documents/budgetview-tauri/src/lib/stores/accounts.ts` - Accounts store\n- `/home/jeremy/Documents/budgetview-tauri/src/lib/stores/transactions.ts` - Transactions store\n- `/home/jeremy/Documents/budgetview-tauri/src/lib/stores/budget.ts` - Budget store\n- `/home/jeremy/Documents/budgetview-tauri/src/lib/components/Sidebar.svelte` - Navigation\n- `/home/jeremy/Documents/budgetview-tauri/src/routes/` - All page components\n- `/home/jeremy/Documents/budgetview-tauri/src/app.css` - Theme & global styles\n\n**Backend:**\n- `/home/jeremy/Documents/budgetview-tauri/src-tauri/src/lib.rs` - Tauri builder\n- `/home/jeremy/Documents/budgetview-tauri/src-tauri/src/commands.rs` - Command handlers\n- `/home/jeremy/Documents/budgetview-tauri/src-tauri/src/db.rs` - Migration loader\n- `/home/jeremy/Documents/budgetview-tauri/src-tauri/migrations/001_initial_schema.sql` - Schema\n- `/home/jeremy/Documents/budgetview-tauri/src-tauri/Cargo.toml` - Rust dependencies\n\n**Configuration:**\n- `/home/jeremy/Documents/budgetview-tauri/package.json` - npm scripts\n- `/home/jeremy/Documents/budgetview-tauri/vite.config.ts` - Vite config\n- `/home/jeremy/Documents/budgetview-tauri/svelte.config.js` - SvelteKit adapter\n- `/home/jeremy/Documents/budgetview-tauri/tsconfig.json` - TypeScript config\n- `/home/jeremy/Documents/budgetview-tauri/src-tauri/tauri.conf.json` - App config\n\n---\n\n### Data Model Summary\n\n**Hierarchies:**\n- Account → Transactions → (Series + SubSeries)\n- BudgetSeries → MonthlyBudget (per year/month)\n- Project → ProjectItems (with series references)\n- CategorizationRules (learned from user actions)\n\n**Key Constraints:**\n- Transactions.series_id is nullable (uncategorized transactions allowed)\n- MonthlyBudget has UNIQUE(series_id, year, month)\n- SubSeries FK cascade delete from BudgetSeries\n- AccountType enum: checking|savings|credit_card|cash\n- BudgetArea enum: income|recurring|variable|extras|savings|transfers\n\nThis codebase is well-structured, follows modern Svelte 5 patterns with runes, has comprehensive database schema, and is ready for Phase 2 implementation (charts/analysis) after the import feature is completed."},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: a0c3f80cfe483d35c (use SendMessage with to: 'a0c3f80cfe483d35c' to continue this agent)\n<usage>total_tokens: 62678\ntool_uses: 42\nduration_ms: 128801</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"85d56d0a-e499-4451-8cdb-61d43ab7f486","uuid":"90e1e232-8264-4bc2-a0bb-733c288217fd","timestamp":"2026-03-17T15:44:34.318Z","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Explore the current state of /home/jeremy/Documents/budgetview-tauri. I need to understand:\n1. What files exist (ls -la the root, src/, src-tauri/src/, src/routes/, src/lib/)\n2. Read the key source files: src-tauri/src/lib.rs, src-tauri/src/commands.rs, src-tauri/src/db.rs, src-tauri/Cargo.toml\n3. Read src/routes/+page.svelte, src/routes/+layout.svelte, src/app.html\n4. Check if migrations exist in src-tauri/migrations/\n5. Read package.json for dependencies\n6. Check src/lib/components/, src/lib/stores/, src/lib/types/, src/lib/utils/ for existing files\n\nBe very thorough - read all these files completely.","agentId":"a0c3f80cfe483d35c","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Now I have a complete understanding of the project. Let me compile a comprehensive report:\n\n## BudgetView-Tauri: Complete Project State Analysis\n\n### Project Overview\nThis is a rewrite of BudgetView (personal budget management software) using **Tauri 2 + SvelteKit + Svelte 5 + SQLite**. The project is in **Phase 1 (MVP)** with scaffolding complete and core MVP features partially implemented.\n\n---\n\n### Directory Structure & Files\n\n#### Root Directory\n**Location:** `/home/jeremy/Documents/budgetview-tauri/`\n\nKey files:\n- `package.json` - Frontend dependencies & build scripts\n- `vite.config.ts` - Vite configuration with Tauri dev host setup\n- `svelte.config.js` - SvelteKit static adapter configuration\n- `tsconfig.json` - TypeScript configuration with strict mode enabled\n- `src/app.css` - TailwindCSS 4 theme with dark mode colors\n- `src/app.html` - HTML template (lang=\"fr\")\n\n---\n\n### Frontend Architecture\n\n#### **src/lib/types/index.ts**\nComplete TypeScript interfaces for:\n- `Account` - Bank accounts (checking, savings, credit card, cash)\n- `BudgetSeries` - Budget categories with budget_area (income/recurring/variable/extras/savings/transfers)\n- `SubSeries` - Subcategories\n- `Transaction` - Individual transactions with categorization\n- `MonthlyBudget` - Monthly budget targets per series\n- `BudgetLineItem` - Aggregated budget view (planned vs actual)\n- `Project` & `ProjectItem` - Savings goals/projects\n- `DashboardSummary` - Key metrics for dashboard\n\n#### **src/lib/utils/format.ts**\n- `formatCurrency()` - French EUR formatting\n- `formatDate()` - French date formatting (DD/MM/YYYY)\n- `formatMonth()` - Localized month/year display\n- Constants: `ACCOUNT_TYPE_LABELS`, `BUDGET_AREA_LABELS`, `BUDGET_AREA_COLORS`\n\n#### **src/lib/stores/** (Svelte 5 reactive stores using `$state`)\n\n**db.ts:**\n- `getDb()` - Singleton database connection to `sqlite:budgetview.db`\n- `query<T>()` - SELECT queries with type safety\n- `execute()` - INSERT/UPDATE/DELETE operations\n\n**accounts.ts - AccountStore:**\n- State: `accounts[]`, `loading`, `error`\n- Methods: `load()`, `create()`, `update()`, `remove()`, `getBalance()`, `totalBalance` (computed)\n\n**transactions.ts - TransactionStore:**\n- State: `transactions[]`, `loading`, `error`, `search`, `filterAccountId`, `filterSeriesId`\n- Methods: `load()` (with filtering), `create()`, `update()`, `categorize()` (with auto-categorization learning), `remove()`\n\n**budget.ts - BudgetStore:**\n- State: `series[]`, `monthlyBudgets[]`, `budgetLines[]`, `loading`, `error`, `year`, `month`\n- Methods: `loadSeries()`, `loadBudgetView()`, `createSeries()`, `updateSeries()`, `removeSeries()`, `setMonthlyBudget()`\n- Computed: `groupedByArea` (grouped by budget_area), `totalPlanned`, `totalActual`\n\n#### **src/lib/components/**\n\n**Sidebar.svelte:**\n- Responsive navigation sidebar with BudgetView branding (blue \"B\" logo)\n- 6 main nav items: Dashboard, Accounts, Transactions, Budget, Analysis, Projects\n- Active link highlighting using `$page.url.pathname`\n- Version display (v0.1.0)\n\n---\n\n### Routes & Pages\n\nAll pages include French `<svelte:head><title>` tags.\n\n#### **src/routes/+layout.svelte**\n- Master layout with sidebar + main content area\n- Flex layout: sidebar (fixed width) + main (flex-1, overflow-y-auto with padding)\n- Imports global `app.css`\n\n#### **src/routes/dashboard/+page.svelte** ✅ (Implemented)\n**Summary Cards:** 4 cards showing:\n- Total balance (Wallet icon)\n- Month income (TrendingUp, green/income color)\n- Month expenses (TrendingDown, red/expense color)\n- Transaction count\n\n**Two-column grid:**\n1. **Accounts Section** - Lists all accounts with type badges and balances\n2. **Recent Transactions** - Last 10 transactions with date/label/amount\n\n**Budget Summary Section:**\n- Conditional: Only shown if budget series exist\n- Displays planned vs actual with progress bars (colored by over/under budget)\n\n**Data Loading:**\n- `onMount()` calls: `accountStore.load()`, `budgetStore.loadBudgetView()`\n- SQL queries for month income/expenses/count via `query()`\n- Recent transactions joined with account names\n\n#### **src/routes/accounts/+page.svelte** ✅ (Implemented)\n**Features:**\n- Total balance display at top\n- Account list cards with edit/delete buttons\n- Modal form for create/edit (name, type, bank, number, initial balance)\n- Account type dropdown using `ACCOUNT_TYPE_LABELS`\n- Responsive grid layout\n- Empty state with Landmark icon\n\n#### **src/routes/transactions/+page.svelte** ✅ (Implemented)\n**Features:**\n- Create/Edit modal form\n- Search bar (live search on Enter key)\n- Filter dropdowns: by account, by category (series)\n- Table view: Date | Label | Account | Category | Amount | Actions\n- Inline categorization popover (click category button to see dropdown)\n- Auto-categorization learning: Saves pattern + series_id to `categorization_rules` table\n- Edit/Delete buttons per row\n- Empty state with Upload icon\n\n**Categorization Logic:**\n- Extracts original_label.toUpperCase() as pattern\n- Upserts into `categorization_rules` with match_count increment\n- Learns from manual categorization for future auto-matching\n\n#### **src/routes/budget/+page.svelte** ✅ (Implemented)\n**Features:**\n- Month navigation (prev/next buttons)\n- Summary cards: Planned | Realized | Remainder\n- Grouped by budget area (income, recurring, variable, extras, savings, transfers)\n- Each category shows:\n  - Inline editable budget amount\n  - Progress bar (color-coded: green=under budget, orange=80%+, red=>100%)\n  - Planned vs Actual amounts\n- Pencil icon to edit series metadata\n- Create new category modal\n\n**Progress Logic:**\n- For income: `actual/planned * 100` (higher is better)\n- For expenses: `abs(actual)/abs(planned) * 100` (lower is better)\n- Over-budget detection and color coding\n\n#### **src/routes/analysis/+page.svelte** ⚠️ (Placeholder)\n- Minimal implementation: \"Pas encore de données\" placeholder\n- Prepared for Phase 2 (Charts section)\n\n#### **src/routes/projects/+page.svelte** ⚠️ (Placeholder)\n- Minimal implementation: \"Aucun projet\" placeholder\n- Prepared for Phase 3 (Projects/savings goals)\n\n---\n\n### Backend (Rust/Tauri)\n\n#### **src-tauri/src/lib.rs**\n```rust\npub fn run() {\n    tauri::Builder::default()\n        .plugin(tauri_plugin_sql with migrations)\n        .plugin(tauri_plugin_log)\n        .invoke_handler([greet])\n        .run()\n}\n```\n\n#### **src-tauri/src/main.rs**\n- Entry point calling `app_lib::run()`\n- Prevents extra console window on Windows\n\n#### **src-tauri/src/commands.rs**\n**Current Commands:**\n- `greet(name: &str) -> String` - Test command returning \"Bienvenue dans BudgetView, {name} !\"\n\n**TODO:** Need to implement actual commands:\n- Account CRUD\n- Transaction CRUD/import\n- Budget operations\n- Series management\n\n#### **src-tauri/src/db.rs**\n```rust\npub fn get_migrations() -> Vec<Migration>\n```\nReturns one migration:\n- Version: 1\n- Description: \"create_initial_tables\"\n- SQL: Loads from `migrations/001_initial_schema.sql`\n\n#### **src-tauri/migrations/001_initial_schema.sql**\nComplete SQLite schema with:\n\n**Core Tables:**\n1. **accounts** - Bank accounts (id, name, account_number, bank_name, account_type, currency, initial_balance, is_active, created_at)\n2. **budget_series** - Budget categories (id, name, budget_area, target_amount, day_of_month, is_active, description)\n3. **sub_series** - Subcategories (id, series_id FK, name)\n4. **transactions** - Individual transactions (id, account_id FK, date, label, original_label, amount, note, is_planned, series_id FK, sub_series_id FK, import_batch_id FK, fitid, created_at)\n5. **transaction_splits** - Multi-category transactions (id, transaction_id FK, series_id FK, amount, note)\n6. **monthly_budget** - Monthly targets per series (id, series_id FK, year, month, planned_amount, UNIQUE constraint)\n\n**Supporting Tables:**\n7. **import_batches** - For rollback capability (id, filename, format IN (ofx/qif/csv), account_id FK, transaction_count, imported_at)\n8. **recurring_transactions** - Templates for recurring transactions (id, account_id FK, label, amount, series_id FK, frequency, day_of_month, start_date, end_date, is_active)\n9. **projects** - Savings goals (id, name, target_amount, target_date, account_id FK, is_active)\n10. **project_items** - Project expenses (id, project_id FK, label, planned_amount, month, year, series_id FK)\n11. **tags** - Transaction tags (id, name UNIQUE)\n12. **transaction_tags** - Tagging junction (transaction_id FK, tag_id FK, PK both)\n13. **categorization_rules** - Auto-categorization patterns (id, pattern UNIQUE, series_id FK, sub_series_id FK, match_count, created_at)\n\n**Pragmas & Indexes:**\n- `PRAGMA journal_mode=WAL` (Write-Ahead Logging for concurrent access)\n- `PRAGMA foreign_keys=ON`\n- Indexes on: transactions.date, transactions.account_id, transactions.series_id, transactions.fitid, monthly_budget.year/month, project_items.project_id\n\n#### **src-tauri/Cargo.toml**\nDependencies:\n- `tauri` 2.10.3 - Core framework\n- `tauri-plugin-log` 2 - Logging\n- `tauri-plugin-sql` 2 (sqlite feature) - Database\n- `sqlx` 0.8 (sqlite + tokio) - SQL toolkit\n- `serde` + `serde_json` - JSON serialization\n- `chrono` 0.4 - Date/time handling\n- `log` 0.4 - Logging trait\n\n**Build Dependencies:**\n- `tauri-build` 2.5.6\n\n#### **src-tauri/tauri.conf.json**\n- App ID: `fr.budgetview.app`\n- Version: 0.1.0\n- Window: 1200x800 (min 900x600), resizable\n- DB preload: `sqlite:budgetview.db`\n- CSP: null (disabled)\n- Bundle targets: all platforms\n\n---\n\n### Package.json Dependencies\n\n**Frontend (Runtime):**\n- `@tauri-apps/api` 2.10.1 - Tauri command invocation & IPC\n- `@tauri-apps/plugin-sql` 2.3.2 - Database access\n- `lucide-svelte` 0.577.0 - 6 icons used (LayoutDashboard, Landmark, ArrowLeftRight, PieChart, BarChart3, FolderKanban, plus many more)\n\n**Dev Dependencies:**\n- `@sveltejs/kit` 2.50.2 - Framework\n- `@sveltejs/adapter-static` 3.0.0 - Static export adapter\n- `svelte` 5.51.0 - Component framework with runes\n- `@sveltejs/vite-plugin-svelte` 6.2.4\n- `@tauri-apps/cli` 2.10.1 - Build tooling\n- `tailwindcss` 4.2.1 - Styling\n- `@tailwindcss/vite` 4.2.1 - Vite plugin\n- `typescript` 5.9.3 - Type checking\n- `vite` 7.3.1 - Build tool\n- `svelte-check` 4.4.2 - Component type checking\n\n---\n\n### Styling\n\n#### TailwindCSS 4 Theme (src/app.css)\n**Color Variables (Dark Mode):**\n- `--color-bg-primary: #0f172a` (very dark blue)\n- `--color-bg-secondary: #1e293b` (dark blue/slate)\n- `--color-bg-card: #1e293b`\n- `--color-bg-hover: #334155` (slate)\n- `--color-border: #334155`\n- `--color-text-primary: #f1f5f9` (off-white)\n- `--color-text-secondary: #94a3b8` (light gray)\n- `--color-text-muted: #64748b` (medium gray)\n- `--color-accent: #3b82f6` (bright blue) / `--color-accent-hover: #2563eb`\n- `--color-success: #22c55e` (green)\n- `--color-warning: #f59e0b` (amber)\n- `--color-danger: #ef4444` (red)\n- `--color-income: #22c55e` (green)\n- `--color-expense: #ef4444` (red)\n\n**Global Styles:**\n- Font: Inter, system-ui (via @theme)\n- h-screen layout, scrollbar styling\n\n---\n\n### Build & Development Commands\n\nFrom `package.json`:\n```bash\nnpm run dev          # Start dev server (vite)\nnpm run build        # Build for production\nnpm run preview      # Preview built app\nnpm run check        # Type checking + svelte-check\nnpm run tauri        # Tauri CLI\n```\n\n**Tauri Dev Flow:**\n1. `beforeDevCommand: \"npm run dev\"` - Starts Vite dev server on port 1420\n2. `beforeBuildCommand: \"npm run build\"` - Builds frontend to `../build/`\n3. Frontend dist copied to `build/` directory\n\n---\n\n### Current Implementation Status\n\n#### ✅ Completed (MVP Phase 1)\n1. **Project Scaffolding** - Tauri 2 + SvelteKit + Svelte 5 + TailwindCSS 4\n2. **Database Schema** - Full SQLite schema with migrations\n3. **Type Definitions** - Complete TypeScript interfaces\n4. **Store/State Management** - Svelte 5 reactive stores with DB integration\n5. **Layout System** - Sidebar + main content layout\n6. **Dashboard Page** - Summary cards, account list, recent transactions, budget overview\n7. **Accounts Page** - CRUD accounts, balance display, modal form\n8. **Transactions Page** - List/search/filter, manual categorization, auto-categorization learning\n9. **Budget Page** - Monthly budget planning, progress visualization, series management\n10. **Utility Functions** - Currency/date formatting, label constants\n\n#### ⚠️ Placeholder/Partial\n1. **Analysis Page** - Skeleton only (Phase 2)\n2. **Projects Page** - Skeleton only (Phase 3)\n\n#### ❌ Not Yet Implemented\n1. **Tauri Commands** - Only `greet()` exists; need CRUD commands for actual backend queries\n2. **Import/Export** - OFX, QIF, CSV import logic (Phase 1 feature, critical for MVP)\n3. **Charts/Visualization** - Chart.js or Layercake integration (Phase 2)\n4. **Recurring Transactions** - Auto-detection logic (Phase 2)\n5. **Projects Management** - CRUD, goal tracking (Phase 3)\n6. **Multi-account Consolidation** - Summary views (Phase 3)\n7. **Encryption** - Password protection (Phase 3)\n8. **Mobile Responsiveness** - Tested but may need refinement\n9. **Error Handling** - Comprehensive error UI feedback\n10. **Accessibility** - ARIA labels, keyboard navigation polish\n\n---\n\n### Key Architectural Decisions\n\n1. **Offline-First** - SQLite embedded, no cloud dependency\n2. **Type-Safe** - TypeScript strict mode + Rust\n3. **Reactive UI** - Svelte 5 runes (`$state`, `$derived`)\n4. **DB Abstraction** - Store layer handles all DB queries\n5. **Auto-Categorization** - Pattern-based learning from user categorization\n6. **Budget Areas** - 6 categories (income/recurring/variable/extras/savings/transfers)\n7. **Monthly Budget Tracking** - Planned vs actual per category per month\n8. **WAL Mode** - SQLite Write-Ahead Logging for concurrency\n\n---\n\n### Next Priority Tasks (from CLAUDE.md Phase 1)\n\n1. **Implement Tauri Commands** for:\n   - Account CRUD (currently store-only)\n   - Transaction CRUD/import (currently store-only)\n   - Budget operations (currently store-only)\n\n2. **Add Import Feature** (OFX/QIF/CSV) - Critical for MVP\n3. **Refine Error Handling** - UI feedback for DB operations\n4. **Test Database Migrations** - Ensure schema creation works\n5. **Build & Package** - Test Tauri build for desktop platforms\n\n---\n\n### File Locations (Absolute Paths)\n\n**Frontend:**\n- `/home/jeremy/Documents/budgetview-tauri/src/lib/types/index.ts` - Types\n- `/home/jeremy/Documents/budgetview-tauri/src/lib/utils/format.ts` - Formatting\n- `/home/jeremy/Documents/budgetview-tauri/src/lib/stores/db.ts` - DB wrapper\n- `/home/jeremy/Documents/budgetview-tauri/src/lib/stores/accounts.ts` - Accounts store\n- `/home/jeremy/Documents/budgetview-tauri/src/lib/stores/transactions.ts` - Transactions store\n- `/home/jeremy/Documents/budgetview-tauri/src/lib/stores/budget.ts` - Budget store\n- `/home/jeremy/Documents/budgetview-tauri/src/lib/components/Sidebar.svelte` - Navigation\n- `/home/jeremy/Documents/budgetview-tauri/src/routes/` - All page components\n- `/home/jeremy/Documents/budgetview-tauri/src/app.css` - Theme & global styles\n\n**Backend:**\n- `/home/jeremy/Documents/budgetview-tauri/src-tauri/src/lib.rs` - Tauri builder\n- `/home/jeremy/Documents/budgetview-tauri/src-tauri/src/commands.rs` - Command handlers\n- `/home/jeremy/Documents/budgetview-tauri/src-tauri/src/db.rs` - Migration loader\n- `/home/jeremy/Documents/budgetview-tauri/src-tauri/migrations/001_initial_schema.sql` - Schema\n- `/home/jeremy/Documents/budgetview-tauri/src-tauri/Cargo.toml` - Rust dependencies\n\n**Configuration:**\n- `/home/jeremy/Documents/budgetview-tauri/package.json` - npm scripts\n- `/home/jeremy/Documents/budgetview-tauri/vite.config.ts` - Vite config\n- `/home/jeremy/Documents/budgetview-tauri/svelte.config.js` - SvelteKit adapter\n- `/home/jeremy/Documents/budgetview-tauri/tsconfig.json` - TypeScript config\n- `/home/jeremy/Documents/budgetview-tauri/src-tauri/tauri.conf.json` - App config\n\n---\n\n### Data Model Summary\n\n**Hierarchies:**\n- Account → Transactions → (Series + SubSeries)\n- BudgetSeries → MonthlyBudget (per year/month)\n- Project → ProjectItems (with series references)\n- CategorizationRules (learned from user actions)\n\n**Key Constraints:**\n- Transactions.series_id is nullable (uncategorized transactions allowed)\n- MonthlyBudget has UNIQUE(series_id, year, month)\n- SubSeries FK cascade delete from BudgetSeries\n- AccountType enum: checking|savings|credit_card|cash\n- BudgetArea enum: income|recurring|variable|extras|savings|transfers\n\nThis codebase is well-structured, follows modern Svelte 5 patterns with runes, has comprehensive database schema, and is ready for Phase 2 implementation (charts/analysis) after the import feature is completed."}],"totalDurationMs":128801,"totalTokens":62678,"totalToolUseCount":42,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":178,"cache_read_input_tokens":57244,"output_tokens":5256,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":178},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
